- âœ… Disclose AI privacy policy clearly â€” especially regarding training data

---

## ğŸ¤– 3. AI Misuse, Cost, and Framing Pitfalls

- âœ… Trim or summarize entries over 2K tokens before AI request
- âœ… Add daily AI quota per user tier + fallback to emoji-only
- âœ… Never state "You alwaysâ€¦" in AI tone â€” use reflective language like "You might notice..."
- âœ… Track average token use per persona type and prompt category

---

## ğŸ’¥ 4. UX Edge Case Handling

- âœ… Block or warn on voice journaling without microphone permission
